text.tspan: UK: Share of COVID-19 tests that are positive
Shown is the percentage of people who received a PCR test in the previous 7 days, who had at least one positive
COVID-19 PCR test result. Data is currently only shown for regions in England.
Source: UK Government COVID-19 Dashboard – Last updated 27 June 2022
